📌 Project Overview
This is Task 2 of the COMP2090 Software Engineering Fundamentals group project. In this task, we independently study and implement two fundamental algorithms/data structures: Shell Sort (an efficient sorting algorithm) and Binary Tree (a hierarchical data structure). The implementation is done in Python, and we provide a detailed report documenting our learning process, analysis, and reflections.
